Read SKILL.md before working in this repository.

This is a defensive secure-code-review skill. Keep all changes aligned with local repository analysis, structured evidence, remediation, and reporting. Do not add exploit scanners, brute-force tools, recon tools, payload fuzzers, unauthorized-access, persistence, evasion, malware, credential-theft, destructive, or real-data-exfiltration behavior.

When editing scripts, preserve structured output and graceful error handling. When editing docs, keep the responsible-use positioning clear.
